channel.title: Need People to help my server
channel.description:
ok....i dont know if this is the right place but yah....i have this awesome server and client....i would love to have people help with it....i tried adding d-claws....but failed..lol....it is playable online...it has i think 1 custom item___i would like help adding more....if u help u will be co-owner.... Just post if u would like to help..... i will only allow 3 people to join
[u]To Join[/u] -post y u want to help -say what u can help with -and how often can u get on
:) :) :) :) :)
